snippet.title: Gartic - The online drawing game
snippet.description:
Welcome to Gartic! It is a free game that invites you to challenge your skills joining a room and trying to guess what players draw. Every turn, one player draw. Simple like that! Join us!

Here is how you can play:

1- Appstore: https://itunes.apple.com/br/app/gartic/id657226057?mt=8
2- Google play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gartic.Gartic&hl=pt_BR
3- PC:  www.gartic.com
4- Windows Phone: https://www.microsoft.com/pt-br/store/p/gartic/9wzdncrfjq7f

Join us!
